 description:
 'Branded hard hats are vinyl decals applied to the shell — never paint, drilling, or heat. Here\'s the ANSI Z89.1 rule on hard hat modifications, why stickers are the only compliant method, and how to spec custom hard hats for a Las Vegas crew.',
 category: 'Compliance',
 readTime: '7 min read',
 date: 'May 9, 2026',
 isoDate: '2026-05-09',
